text: Lakewood High School is a public high school in Hebron, Ohio, United States. Their athletic teams are known as the Lancers. ==State championships== * Boys Baseball – 1993, 1994, 2005 * Girls Softball - 2008, 2009, 2010, 2016, 2017 ==Notes and references== ==External links== * Category:High schools in Licking County, Ohio Category:Public high schools in Ohio
title: Lakewood High School (Hebron, Ohio)
